 x 
 a^{x} \stackrel{\text{def}}{=} \exp(x \ln(a)). 
 \lim_{y \to x} \exp(y \ln(a)) = \exp \left( \lim_{y \to x} y \ln(a) \right) = \exp(x \ln(a)), 
 \lim_{y \to x} a^{y} = a^{x}. 
